HEADWORD: Air stove
<hw>Air" stove`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>A stove for heating a current
of air which is directed against its surface by means of pipes, and then
distributed through a building.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

